238
00:14:41,860 --> 00:14:45,140
measure it in hemoglobin A1C.

239
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:48,860
It binds at positions 66 and 110.

240
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:54,540
Now the hemoglobin A1C assay is not set up to look at 66 and 110.

241
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:57,020
This requires a major research lab.

242
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,320
It requires tandem mass spec.

243
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,320
It's a huge undertaking.

244
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:07,140
It's only done as a research tool and the only lab I know that does it is in Japan.

245
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:12,220
